{"tid":2436412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"另一航界政治犯—譚文豪","createTime":"2021-03-07T06:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:41:57.000Z","uid":68125,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6f4da885cbaccbdf6bf9963be89cb134b10c45","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1525652564304306/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1525652564304306%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=5a290f5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1525652564304306/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mM1Zvb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmM1Zvb6.jpg&h=4bc543b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有留意或任職香港航空界的讀者，相信都會聽過三個涉足政界的航業界人士，其中兩位&mdash;即前英國航空 (BA) 空中服務員吳敏兒及前國泰航空 (CX) 機長譚文豪已經未審先囚，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">成為政治犯以作對西方盟國談判條件的籌碼</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n根據庭上自辯及之前訪問，前國泰航空 (CX) 機長譚文豪<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">生於草根，於葵涌木屋區出身，其父為的士司機</span></span>。其後譚機長<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">為改變政策及創造機會，不惜減少收入投身政界</span></span>，終於成功由草根脫離世代貧窮，可惜父親末期大腸癌離世。譚機長為了能家庭團聚保釋，所以決定退出公民黨。<br />\n<br />\n另外吳敏兒是前英國航空 (BA) 空中服務員，在公眾場合或私下閒聊都絕少提家事，但在庭上由律師口中得知吳小姐基於前夫離開香港，所以與吳小姐離婚，現時與女兒及母親同住。<br />\n<br />\n如果有去過職工盟記者會的話，都會聽到吳小姐言明不會做違法的事，故2019年時基於機場禁制令生效下，國泰城集合最終改為郵政總局對出舉行。<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">吳小姐希望能保釋照顧家人</span></span>及身體，不惜退出加入6年的工黨，同時辭任職工盟主席。<br />\n<br />\n最後兩位如黎智英案一樣，都<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不能保釋要繼續還押</span></span>。"},{"pid":"9e8e88aab2a28f5f8a6104a703c5c6f3b484a273","tid":2436412,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"個page係咪你嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791c2e780f0cb357ece4113e268c2e099ca0768e","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c15c83415dc483fb164c77c229047eacad67aac","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7901cb309508e17bf810bf73cce9180503e58c32","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:39:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0de305efdf54c8d031385f499127772be813df1","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"629a360a66a89f211faacdd126f2ae72b9aeb0f6","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8639529b2c19748bbe2f65d2dd47a3f970d53df3","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7846929e06ffad35a2decd9d200cb7fb4e90bf0","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2298c3310cd31cad56277bde834750d4d21c981","tid":2436412,"uid":272094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />含淚推"},{"pid":"e07cb4566f3cd837fa27ef230df670cdea2b8de1","tid":2436412,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}